CASE		WHEN NVL(RM_DPD, 0) <= 5 THEN 0
			WHEN NVL(RM_DPD, 0) > 5 AND NVL(RM_DPD, 0) <= 29 THEN 1
			WHEN NVL(RM_DPD, 0) > 29 AND NVL(RM_DPD, 0) <= 59 THEN 2
			WHEN NVL(RM_DPD, 0) > 59 AND NVL(RM_DPD, 0) <= 89 THEN 3
			WHEN NVL(RM_DPD, 0) > 89 AND NVL(RM_DPD, 0) <= 119 THEN 4
			WHEN NVL(RM_DPD, 0) > 119 AND NVL(RM_DPD, 0) <= 149 THEN 5
			WHEN NVL(RM_DPD, 0) > 149 AND NVL(RM_DPD, 0) <= 179 THEN 6
			WHEN NVL(RM_DPD, 0) > 179 THEN 7 END AS RM_DPD,RM_OVRD,RM_FLG FROM (
SELECT DISTINCT SHADOW_ACNO AS ProviderContractNo,CAST(NVL(DPD_13JUN,0) AS VARCHAR(10)) RM_DPD ,CAST(NVL(OD_13JUN,0) AS VARCHAR(20))  RM_OVRD, 'Y' As RM_FLG 
FROM 
(SELECT DISTINCT SHADOW_ACNO ,DPD_13JUN DPD_13JUN ,OD_13JUN ,CD_PROD_CODE FROM 
(SELECT DISTINCT FINAL.*,
CASE WHEN (DPD>0 and MAY_DDA='YES' and DDA_PRESENT='NO' 
and JUN_DPD = 0) then 1 
WHEN (DPD>0 AND BAL>=CURRENT_CIF_OD
)  then 1
ELSE 0 
END FLAG 
FROM 
(
SELECT ALL_CON.*,
CASE WHEN MAY.CONTRACT_REF_NO IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO'
END AS MAY_DDA,
CASE WHEN JUN.CONTRACT_REF_NO IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO'
END AS JUN_DDA,
CASE WHEN JUL.CONTRACT_REF_NO IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO'
END AS JUL_DDA,
CASE WHEN CLEAR_DDA_19JUN.CONTRACT_REF_NO IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO'
END AS CLEAR_DDA_19JUN,
CASE WHEN CLEAR_DDA_YES.CONTRACT_REF_NO IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO'
END AS CLEAR_DDA_YES,
CASE WHEN DDA_PRESENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO IS NOT NULL THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO'
END AS DDA_PRESENT,
MAY_SAL.MAY_SAL,
JUN_SAL.JUN_SAL,
JUL_SAL.JUL_SAL,
RTL_BAL.BAL
FROM 
(SELECT * FROM 
dmp_temp.ALL_CONT_RTL)
ALL_CON
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM dmp_temp.DDA_THREE_MONTH
WHERE SETTLEMENTDATE BETWEEN '2024-05-01' AND '2024-05-31') MAY ON ALL_CON.SHADOW_ACNO= MAY.CONTRACT_REF_NO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM dmp_temp.DDA_THREE_MONTH
WHERE SETTLEMENTDATE BETWEEN '2024-06-01' AND '2024-06-30') JUN ON ALL_CON.SHADOW_ACNO= JUN.CONTRACT_REF_NO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM dmp_temp.DDA_THREE_MONTH
WHERE SETTLEMENTDATE BETWEEN '2024-07-01' AND CURRENT_DATE-1 ) JUL ON ALL_CON.SHADOW_ACNO= JUL.CONTRACT_REF_NO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM DMP_TEMP.DDA_19JUN
WHERE SETTLEMENTDATE BETWEEN '2024-06-19' AND CURRENT_DATE-1 ) CLEAR_DDA_19JUN ON ALL_CON.SHADOW_ACNO= CLEAR_DDA_19JUN.CONTRACT_REF_NO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM DMP_TEMP.DDA_19JUN
WHERE SETTLEMENTDATE =CURRENT_DATE-1 ) CLEAR_DDA_YES ON ALL_CON.SHADOW_ACNO= CLEAR_DDA_YES.CONTRACT_REF_NO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM 
DMP_TEMP.DDA_PRESENT  ) DDA_PRESENT ON ALL_CON.SHADOW_ACNO= DDA_PRESENT.CONTRACT_REF_NO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT V_CUSTOMER_CODE,SUM(TOTALSAL) AS MAY_SAL 
FROM DMP_TEMP.ALL_MON_SAL
WHERE D_TRN_DT BETWEEN '2024-05-01' AND '2024-05-31'
GROUP BY V_CUSTOMER_CODE)MAY_SAL ON ALL_CON.CIF=MAY_SAL.V_CUSTOMER_CODE
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT V_CUSTOMER_CODE,SUM(TOTALSAL) AS JUN_SAL 
FROM DMP_TEMP.ALL_MON_SAL
WHERE D_TRN_DT BETWEEN '2024-06-01' AND '2024-06-30'
GROUP BY V_CUSTOMER_CODE)JUN_SAL ON ALL_CON.CIF=JUN_SAL.V_CUSTOMER_CODE

LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT V_CUSTOMER_CODE,SUM(TOTALSAL) AS JUL_SAL 
FROM DMP_TEMP.ALL_MON_SAL
WHERE D_TRN_DT BETWEEN '2024-07-01' AND CURRENT_DATE-1
GROUP BY V_CUSTOMER_CODE)JUL_SAL ON ALL_CON.CIF=JUL_SAL.V_CUSTOMER_CODE
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM  DMP_TEMP.ALL_BAL)RTL_BAL ON  ALL_CON.CIF=RTL_BAL.CIF
) FINAL 
) MAIN WHERE FLAG=1 and cd_prod_code not in ('HFTM','HOMEFIN','HFDL')



UNION

)  then 1

LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT V_CUSTOMER_CODE,SUM(TOTALSAL) AS JUN_SAL 
FROM DMP_TEMP.ALL_MON_SAL
WHERE D_TRN_DT BETWEEN '2024-06-01' AND '2024-06-30'
GROUP BY V_CUSTOMER_CODE)JUN_SAL ON BASE.CIF=JUN_SAL.V_CUSTOMER_CODE
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT V_CUSTOMER_CODE,SUM(TOTALSAL) AS JUL_SAL 
FROM DMP_TEMP.ALL_MON_SAL
WHERE D_TRN_DT BETWEEN '2024-07-01' AND CURRENT_DATE-1
GROUP BY V_CUSTOMER_CODE)JUL_SAL ON BASE.CIF=JUL_SAL.V_CUSTOMER_CODE
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM  DMP_TEMP.ALL_BAL)RTL_BAL ON  BASE.CIF=RTL_BAL.CIF
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT DISTINCT SHADOW_ACNO,OD_13JUN,DPD_13JUN
FROM DMP_TEMP.PRE_13JUN WHERE CS_PRODUCT IN ('HFTM','HFDL','HOMEFIN')) PRE13_JUN ON BASE.ACNO=PRE13_JUN.SHADOW_ACNO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT DISTINCT SHADOW_ACNO,DPD 
FROM DMP_TEMP.MAY_FULLPF WHERE CS_PRODUCT IN ('HFTM','HFDL','HOMEFIN')) MAY_FULLPF ON BASE.ACNO=MAY_FULLPF.SHADOW_ACNO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT DISTINCT SHADOW_ACNO,DPD 
FROM DMP_TEMP.JUN_FULLPF WHERE CS_PRODUCT IN ('HFTM','HFDL','HOMEFIN')) JUN_FULLPF ON BASE.ACNO=JUN_FULLPF.SHADOW_ACNO
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT DISTINCT SHADOW_ACNO,DPD 
FROM DMP_TEMP.JUL_FULLPF WHERE CS_PRODUCT IN ('HFTM','HFDL','HOMEFIN')) JUL_FULLPF ON BASE.ACNO=JUL_FULLPF.SHADOW_ACNO
) MAIN
) FINAL WHERE FLAG=1 
 ) WHERE SHADOW_ACNO  IN (SELECT ACNO FROM DMP_TEMP.REQ1_OLD_BOOK) AND DPD_13JUN IS NOT  NULL

 )
